> ===Literature=== 
* Doris Croissant: Visions of the Third Princess. Gendering spaces in The Tale of Genji illustrations. Arts asiatiques. Vol. 60 (2005): 103-120 [[@http://www.persee.fr/web/revues/home/prescript/article/arasi_0004-3958_2005_num_60_1_1533|pdf]]
* [[Alexander Coburn Soper]]: The Illustrative Method of the Tokugawa "Genji" Pictures. The Art Bulletin , Vol. 37, No. 1 (Mar., 1955), pp. 1-16 [[@http://www.jstor.org/stable/3047589|jstor]]

